item.title: 1090 IONQ
item.description: score:1090 Chances: IonQ is an industry leader in quantum computing, and its recent MOU with South Korea’s Ministry of Science and ICT may boost its presence in the Asian quantum computing industry. The company has increased its 2023 bookings expectations by 25% and is expecting more than 100% growth in bookings compared to last year’s performance.
